| What               | Annotation                       | Reason                 |
| ------------------ | -------------------------------- | ---------------------- |
| Dio                | `@module` + `@lazySingleton`     | Central config & reuse |
| Retrofit Service   | `@lazySingleton` + factoryMethod | Inject Dio cleanly     |
| Remote Data Source | `@LazySingleton(as: ...)`        | One per feature        |
| Repository         | `@LazySingleton(as: ...)`        | Shared instance        |
| UseCases / Bloc    | `@injectable`                    | New instance if needed |
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------